Pascal Okechukwu, popular socialite fondly called Cubana Chief Priest, says he has gifted his wife a G-Wagon for her birthday He took to his Instagram page to share images of the vehicle, stating, “Asked my woman what she wants for her birthday, she said get me a Benz, it’s few days to her bday so I called @naijacarshop and he made it happen, congrats baby it’s a fucking G-class of the 63’s above all it’s a freaky AMG, now you can roar like a lioness that you are. I hope she likes it because e no easy to impress rich aunty.” Okechukwu was recently appointed as the special adviser to the governor of Imo State on social media influence and social events management. The entertainer is known for displaying opulence on social media. 